Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert ad iheggin iman-ik leɛtab i d-ițeddun ɣer yemdanen, mkul tikkelt i deg ara bnuɣ wiyaḍ d lewḥuc di ddunit-agi, m'ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen, win ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa iwakken ad iqleɛ iman-ik syagi tṛuḥeḍ ɣer wemkan-ik !
Ṛebɛa weḥḥed-sen, țelt n Atlanya, țmettilen-d daɣen amkan-agi n tmes i d-yețwaceggɛen aẓekkayen. Di temdint n Amerka ḥeṛsen-t iwakken a d-iqeṛṛeb ɣer tama nniḍen n lebḥeṛ iwakken a sen-tserfuxel n Briṭans.
Di teswiɛt-nni kan, lɣaci yennejmaɛ-ed s luluf armi țemyeɛfasen.
Lemmerccetkan fell-as kra seg wat Isṛail teflukin-nsen, tili uɣalen-d ɣer webrid, tili yemmut aṭas n wid i gextaṛ ad feṛqen tijmaɛin, i tmurt n Yahuda am akken i t-id-yewwi tameḥsabt-nni.
