Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tazmert ad ɣelqen abrid-nsen, meɛna m'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, ad lemden awren lǧețța-nsen. Axaṭer lemmer ț-țideț ayen i d-yeqqimen seg-s, tili setɛeṛfen belli d iqelwacen deg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen.
Imi ayagi akk i gmetlen ayen yellan d lɛaddat-agi, ilaq a ten-yaf zeddigen s tmeslayt ; ula d lsas n leḥmadiyen yellan di temdint n Lquds :
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni, ssawḍen-as-t ɣer tezzenz.
