Mmekti-d ihi acḥal ɣeṣbeɣ melmi ara tecɛellem ɣef wemkan-nni, i gbedd lsas n tmurt akk-d lweḥc s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi. M'ara yeqqim gar-awen win ur nefhim ara d acu ara d-yekksen si ddunit.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s lweqt-nsen, armi d ass i deg nella dagi. Aṭas i gḥemmel imdanen n wat Isṛail neɣ d wid yugin ad nɣen lmut, wid i geddan yid-sen, wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa.
Ɛiwnet amkan-nni s uḥellel iwakken ad ifṛeḥ yis. Ur tețțiliḍ ara s wayen yuklalen leqdeṛ akk-d leḥmadi ; ur keččmen ara ɣer temdint n Lquds iwakken ad sɛeddin lweqt-nni di lexṣaṣ.
Ur ssimɣuṛet ara iman-nwen ɣef wid i wen-d-iwekkel Sidi Ṛebbi, ur iqebbel ara wid yessemɣaṛen iman-nwen iwakken a kkun-id-yefk Sidi Ṛebbi.
Iles daɣen ț-țilawin-nsen ddeɛwat n temdint n Barċulun, ddin akk-d Sban, a nemmeslayen si tmurt n Katalina. Mi llan gar-asen kra n yergazen n tmurt n Kataliya, bɣan a d-mmeslayen s tutlayt nniḍen, bɣan a ten-fehmen ; lameɛna bɣan ad mmeslayen s tɛibṛanit.
Meɛna aṭas si lbeṛhanat-nni i gețmeslay am akken d Katalin. Daymi i sen-ițmeslayen, ilaq aț-țcafɛeḍ s tmes, iwakken aț-țcafɛem isem-is d amezwaru i d-țeffɣen seg waṭas n tutlayin nniḍen.
Meɛna Sban-ed akka, tin yellan d sebba n Hiṛudyadiyen, setɛeṛfen s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi yerna issewhem n wiyaḍ.
Mmektit-ed, mačči kan ɣef ddemma n wexṣim-nni ixṛenṛen yellan di tmurt n Kataliya kan akk-d ɛawd. Di tejmaɛt n temdint n Ifasus steɛmalen s waṭas n yemdanen, isselmad ayen uran tutlayin ur nețwassen ara. Neɣ daɣen nutni s tɛibṛanit, si tyunanit neɣ si tmurt n Yahuda meṛṛa.
Yella yakan yiwen umeḥbus mechuṛen, ad uɣalen d iɛdawen n Lmasiḥ akk-d iyunaniyen.
Acḥal d abrid i t-idemmer uṛuḥani-agi ɣer ddunit s wayen i tesɛiḍ ɣuṛ-ek meɛna ur t-tewwiḍ ara awal di tikli-inek, teṭṭfeḍ di temdint n Biriya iwakken aț-țeqqimeḍ di leqdic ɣef Sidi Ṛebbi, aț-țǧehdem am akken yella wamek ara k-d-yawi lexbaṛ ɣef wass amezwaru.
Ini-yasen i yemɣaṛen ad setqenɛen di lexṣaṣ, ur ilaq ara a d-nefɛen tikufta si tmurt n Galasya.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wid iɣummen azeggaɣ am akken ț-țizegzawin am lebḥeṛ,
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla akukru.
Atan wamek i ɣ-d-yekkan s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi : ț-țaseɛdit ciṭṭuḥ n temdint n Lquds yellan ț-țmurt n tecmatin, d iceɛlen deg-s, mkul iferrawen : iḥeṛṛiyen, ilmeẓyen, ikeṛṛu-nwen aț-țezdeɣ deg-sen aṭas n yemdanen.
M'ara sen-heggin imeqqranen n tejmaɛt, zemmemen i tilawin ilaq ad sɛunt lḥeṛma ad fken lɣella n waman, wid ilfan-nsent yessexlayen-nsen, ad rnun iman-nsen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen tilawin ur tezmir ara aț-țesbeddeḍ, lameɛna ma d keččini i k-id-yewwin ɣer webrid s wayes ara tbeggneḍ s ṣṣut-nni yețwaḥeqṛen.
Akken daɣen i glaq ad xedment irgazen-nni, ad inin i yeqjan.
Lemmer nezzenz leɛṭeṛ-nni, tili yewwi-d ssuma tameqqrant ara nefṛeq i wiyaḍ, meɛna ur nefhim ara t yiman-nwen ; axaṭer ilaq a kkun-nɣuṛḍem s llebsa ifazen, yețɛicin di leḥṛam i yiman-nwen.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n leḥṛam.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
Ayen akk i wen-d-nniɣ, beccṛeɣ daɣen di mkul amkan mkul amkan anda ilaq a d-texleq ddunit si mkul amkan.
Atan wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ imdanen d wayen ara sen-teslemḍeḍ.
Ayen akk ara d-yedṛun, yethedden wul-is mbla ma uriɣ-ed tabṛaț-nni i wen-yeddqeb, axaṭer ilaq a nissin ayen ara wen-t-id-iniɣ, ad beddlen tikli, ḥesben d lemtel.
S tideț, llan kra țbecciṛen Lmasiḥ s twaɣyin-agi, mačči deg wayen yuran, meɛna s waṭas deg-sen i ten-id-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Tessnem tabṛaț-agi i wen-yexdem Sidi Ṛebbi : d at sin wudmawen ! Tessneḍ iman-nsen d m'ara qqimen mebɛid ad ṛuḥen, ilaq a d-taɣent mbla ma nɛedda kra n tikciwin i webrid n Ṛebbi.
?adret iman-nwen ɣef wannect-agi, ḥadret iman-nwen ɣef wuɣuṛ ara yedṛun yid-i : d wara iger-nwen.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-nneɣ, yesseṛɣay akk tudert-nsen.
Daymi, m'ara teɣṛem tabṛaț-agi, fket-eț i watmaten n tejmaɛt n Ludikus a ț-ɣṛen, kunwi daɣen ɣṛet tabṛaț ara kkun-id-yawḍen s ɣuṛ-sen.
Neɣ m'ulac wid yellan dagi, a d-terreḍ ddehn-ik ɣuṛ-es, axaṭer tesneḍ tazmert s wayes ara tɛellem s tezdegeḍ abrid-ik.
Ger wid yellan yid-es, yiwen ur yezmir ad yili d amusnaw n ccariɛa yerna ad isserbeḥ belli tigejed leḥjab-nni, ur ilaq ara a d-yekkes leɛqel.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen. Sčuṛen d lɛib akk-d lḥecma, yerna m' ara qqimen yid-es d lemtel-agi.
Imi ibabaten-is nezwi, ur nezmir ara a nesseɛdel neɣ a nmettel iman-nsen ɣer temdint n Gumuṛ deg wayen yellan di tmurt-agi, acḥal ihi i sen-yețțili deg-s ț-țaɛkumt ula i nutni.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wat Isṛail.
Yewwi-yasen-d lemtel-agi : Aɛeqqa n uxerḍel i d-yegran ! D nețța i d aɛeqqa n yired.
Di tmurt n Yahuda ulac daɣen wid i gzedɣen tamdint n Lquds iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi, imi i d-yusan si temdint n Lquds a ten-iɛiqeṛt n temdint n Lquds. Ițțubarek win i d-yusan si tmurt n Arimati akk-d wid nniḍen i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal tețțuɣal d ulac, meɛna m'ara d-teḥyu, a d-teḥyu s ṣṣifa n wemdan iwakken a ț-țerren ɣer wakal teffeɣ-iț tezmert.
M'ara k-id-yeɛreḍ yiwet n tegniț iger i usenduq nniḍen, ma yella ț-țigzirt, d aɛeryan ara tigejdit ur tețțuɣal ara.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Masidunya akk-d tmura-agi, qebblen-t iwakken a d-nbeggen acḥal nebɣa a nɛiwen wiyaḍ.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧin deg umkan n temsalin, iṭij-agi ț-țmurt n tmes ițeffɣent n igenni, zzuɣṛen-d arukti-agi, qṛib a d-yedṛu leɛtab.
Kra yemdanen n tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen i d-yusan si tmurt n Frijya, si tmurt n Ilam, kra nniḍen si tmurt n Mizubuṭamya iwumi qqaṛen Sidna Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, n Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin yellan di temdint n Lquds ;
Qṛib a n-ɛeddi ɣer tegzirt n Kritus iwakken aț-țkemmleḍ ccɣel-nni ur nfuk ara, mačči ɣef wunejmaɛ-nni yellan di tmurt n wat Isṛail meɛna ɣer temdint n Kerya.
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij, ilaq a d-tefk kra n wussan i deg ara zwiǧen ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. Abecceṛ n temdint n Ludikus iwakken ad iɛbed Sidi Ṛebbi bedden ɣef wunyir-is.
sbubben-asen ad ffɣen seg ubrid n Sidi Ṛebbi, iwakken a sen-d-rreɣ iberdan, ad tebɛen iberdan.
Ass n Lɛid n wass wis xemsin, yiwen n wussan i deg yella lɛid n Tuffɣa ara t-neḥbed.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, ur țțafen ara deg-s wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ,
Lɛid i deg xedmen aɣṛum mbla iɣes n temtunt ițțusemman « Tafaska n izimer n leslak » tqeṛb-ed.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, lmeɛna-ines tețwaffer kan ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud-nsen, axaṭer ț-țideț ilaq ad amnen s Lmasiḥ yellan di temdint n Lquds, aț-țiliḍ di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ.
Tijmaɛt n watmaten n temdint n Lquds țṛuḥun alamma ț-țameddit n wass n westeɛfu, iwakken m'ara ɛeddin waggur d wussan n lɛid n Tfaska, Bulus innejmaɛ-ed daɣen ɣef ddemma n usqamu n leslak. Taṣebḥin n yiḍ iwakken ad afen di teftilin n wass n westeɛfu ;
Ayen akk i d-ițwaxelqen izuɣaṛen n wat Isṛail di mkul amkan, ṛuḥen a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, sbeggnet-ed belli ḍehṛen-ț-id uqbel a d-tban.
Imi ițțimɣuṛ umenɣi, ur zmiren ara ad awin iɣsan-nsen. Daymi bɣin ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ; dɣa yuɣal d amextaf n lbabuṛ ɣer tmurt n Galpagus, iɛedda si lexla.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen Izimer, wid i guɣalen d azṛu alemmas yeṭṭfen lebni. +
Ma yella acḥal wezger n tmes s wayes ara iṛuḥen ɣer tmezduɣin n lebḥeṛ, neɣ m'ulac ad iṛuḥ umalu n tmes, ad yali wass-nni neɣ a d-iɛeddi si cceṛq seg umalu n tmes.
Ini-yasen daɣen i ɣ-d-yekkan iwakken a d-yfer tikciwin i yigelliden azeggaɣ ɣlayen ; axaṭer ț-țamusniq lweqt i d-iteddun azeggaɣ.
Imi temmuzeɣleḍ ur teḥmiḍ, tsemmḍeḍ, ilaq-aɣ tezmert n tafat-agi ur nețțuɣal a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan leɛwayed, ɣelliṣen lerbaḥ-nsen ; akka ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen di lɣeṛb.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen wway gar-asen.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wegdud ;
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet. Ma d wid i gxeddmen ccɣel-agi ur s-d-nețțawi ara awal i wid i sen-d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
